Company Overview of Fundamental Global Investors, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Fundamental Global Investors, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to high net worth individuals, other investment advisers, and private funds for sophisticated, qualified investors, including high net worth individuals, pension plans, funds of funds, family offices, endowments, and other institutions. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and commodity portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, and commodity markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests in value stocks of companies. It employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolio. Fundamental Global Investors, LLC was founded in 2012, and is based in Mo...
Fundamental Global Investors, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to high net worth individuals, other investment advisers, and private funds for sophisticated, qualified investors, including high net worth individuals, pension plans, funds of funds, family offices, endowments, and other institutions. The firm manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and commodity portfolios. It invests in the public equity, fixed income, and commodity markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests in value stocks of companies. It employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolio. Fundamental Global Investors, LLC was founded in 2012, and is based in Mooresville, North Carolina; with an additional office in Naples, Florida.
